---
title: Honey-Soy & Ginger Double Pork Meatballs with Ponzu Pear Slaw & Peanuts
description: Fragrance, aromas and flavours, we can tick all those boxes with these pork meatballs. The honey-soy glaze adds a touch of sweet and salty goodness, a perfect match for pork mince. That’s a wrap on our dinner to-do list!

